@SysInclude { doc }
@SysInclude { svgmacros }
@Doc @Text @Begin
@PP
Four-node Mermaid flowchart routed through the @Mermaid macro.
The PostScript reference rendering is a placeholder note; the
SVG render places a div.mermaid inside a foreignObject for
mermaid.js to engrave at view-time.  Lines inside the literal
are separated with octal newlines so Lout's lexer accepts the
string -- mermaid parses newlines or semicolons interchangeably.
@LP
@Mermaid { "flowchart TD\012A[Start] --> B{Ready?}\012B -->|Yes| C[Run]\012B -->|No| D[Wait]" }
@End @Text
